撚抗爭，你班毒撚喺屋企做乜拎嘢，毒撚打J打死，仆街死</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">721 <br />\n伯伯絕食咁老都出黎為下一代你班毒撚抗爭，你班毒撚喺屋企做乜拎嘢，打J打死佢仆街</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">721 <br />\n維園見</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPVE1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPVE1p1.jpg&h=85169db2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJKZgYp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJKZgYp.png&h=a385323f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">721 <br />\n維園見</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZHoJDs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZHoJDs.png&h=33b00c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">721 <br />\n維園見</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCC0M4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCC0M4H.jpg&h=e628e7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住，親中暴徒、黑社會無論咩時期都係社會渣<br />\n滓，任何人攻擊佢地都唔會失去道德高地，大家盡情打，放手打，打死兩個當一雙，可以用任何形式羞辱佢地<br />\n<br />\n呢班人全部都係收錢做野既僱傭兵，即使上到戰場都唔會受日內瓦公約保障，大家用任何非人道方法虐待佢地都唔會有任何後果。因為佢地本身就係不法之徒，唔會敢上庭做證，就算上庭佢地都係不可信證人，驚佢老母</span>"},{"pid":"fe8